{"tid":1136450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食環署外判清潔工的悲涼","createTime":"2019-05-03T04:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T07:45:08.000Z","uid":100299,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"384106aa742d19398700ebc5ddd53bbfb3e90a45","tid":1136450,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:20:28.000Z","msg":"本人是離職食環署外判蟲治清潔工人&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉！政府啲外判工已經好L刻薄啦，還有嗰班科文更仆街，以權謀私收規外，更加用權力欺壓自己下屬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事缘最近從中西區舊同事口中得知，灣仔惡霸陳氏三兄弟，其三兄弟不嬲係灣仔横行霸道。而今次主角係兄弟中嘅三陪，佢為人不知所謂，係今年年初見一替位女工樣貌娟好，即時起痰兼調換原本的女工走，繼而安排此娟好的女工在他的隊伍工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就此三陪不斷向女工獻殷勤及不時抽人水，但女工對他的行為極為厭惡，已經處處迴避。三陪也不斷將車隊中原來的員工調走，用散工代替，以孤立此女工而方便他的淫行&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜而家嘅香港墮落到如此地步，真係無眼睇&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n1"},{"pid":"b60e8beb084294972b18c9992129e15aec158501","tid":1136450,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:21:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=28193645#pid498691416&amp;utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_medium=share&amp;utm_campaign=msite\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Faction%3Dthread%26tid%3D28193645%23pid498691416%26utm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_medium%3Dshare%26utm_campaign%3Dmsite&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=0eb48ca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=28193645#pid498691416&amp;utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_medium=share&amp;utm_campaign=msite</a>"},{"pid":"ce30cce3b698291963a2c0285d612644120f2dbb","tid":1136450,"uid":209543,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:54:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f17dc322cea04ea21eb3e463d60349bddd64cf8","tid":1136450,"uid":209543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1424e44ccd4d5ed2c3fbb9b92d0922bd590051d","tid":1136450,"uid":209543,